<h1 style="font-size:35;">The Transformers</h1>

<div class="content">
    
    <p1 style="text-align: center">
<!-- Informativ text -->
    <h2>The Autobots</h2>

    The Autobots are one of two factions in the Cybertronian War. <br>
    They fight to protect humans from the evil The Decepticons. founded by Prima, The Autobots' leader is Optimus Prime.
    <br> <b> <h2>History</h2></b> 
    Before the time of the transformers, the Creators used deadly bombs called Seeds to turn planets’ organic life into their elemental metal <br>
    in order to create a powerful godlike cube called the AllSpark. <br>
    Sometime later, the AllSpark first created seven Primes.
   
</p1>

<p2>
    The seven leaders set out into the universe seeking distant suns to harvest and create Energon <br>
    by building powerful machines called Star Harvesters on the planets that were the closest to them. <br>
    The Primes set out with a rule: Never destroy a planet with life. <br>
    It means to never harvest a sun with an inhabited planet. <br>
    Until one of them tried to defy that rule and his name forevermore was the Fallen  <br>
    due to him despising the human race and desire to exterminate humanity <br>
    by starting off with ordering the construction of a Star Harvester on Earth in order to destroy both the planet and its sun. <br>
    The only way to activate the machine is with a legendary key called the Matrix of Leadership, <br>
    which he stole from the Primes after tricking them to come to Earth in order to do so.  <br> 
</p2>
<br>
<br>

